WEBVTT

00:00:07.680 --> 00:00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

00:01:37.160 --> 00:01:42.840
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL <i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:01.920
WANGCHENG

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.200
They came well-prepared.

00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:05.760
They mean to trap us like rats.

00:02:05.840 --> 00:02:07.000
Report!

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.400
Report! The Northern Desert has stationed 1,500 troops at the North Gate,

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:12.960
And at the East, West, and South Gates, 500 troops each.

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:14.600
Not many.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:16.240
Seriously?

00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:18.000
Wangcheng has only 500 garrison troops.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:20.600
How can we defeat 3,000 elite troops from the Northern Desert?

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.880
The battle hasn't even begun. Stop spoiling the morale.

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:26.520
Do you think the 300 soldiers I brought along are good for nothing?

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:29.000
Wangcheng, sheltered by Yunzhong Prefecture,

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.200
Has grown soft.

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:32.120
How could your defenses be this lax?

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:34.360
Not even 800 could withstand 3,000.

00:02:34.440 --> 00:02:35.360
Nonsense.

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:38.680
Those 800 soldiers could rout all 3,000 of them.

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:43.240
If you disrupt morale again, I'll offer your head to our banner.

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:47.360
So many troops crossed the border, yet not a single word leaked out?

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:49.240
Who else could it be but Xiao Xun?

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:53.000
He opened the gates to foreign aggression.

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:57.080
Since they stationed 500 troops at the East, West, and South Gates each,

00:02:57.160 --> 00:02:59.720
As long as we concentrate our forces and break out from the South Gate,

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:01.640
There is a chance to escort Your Highness out.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:02.960
Exactly, Zhao.

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:05.080
Leave now, and we will hold the rear.

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:06.920
Even at the cost of my life, I will get you out of the city.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:08.480
No. I cannot leave.

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:12.600
We cannot let the people of Wangcheng fall victim to the enemy's blades.

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:15.200
Nor can we let Xiao Xun's scheme succeed.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:17.880
Wangcheng lies behind Yunzhong.

00:03:18.480 --> 00:03:20.160
If the Northern Desert takes Wangcheng,

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:22.760
The Lord of Xiaonan will surely seize the chance to march.

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:25.480
They will then be able to pincer Yunzhong Prefecture.

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:28.000
By then, the State of Chu will inevitably plunge into chaos,

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:29.760
Allowing Xiao Xun to usurp the throne.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:34.200
Therefore, Wangcheng must not fall, and I shall not leave.

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.560
Are you alright?

00:03:37.480 --> 00:03:39.280
Madam Ge, what brings you here?

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.600
And who are you people?

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.760
Wangcheng's gates have been completely sealed

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:47.680
By the Northern Desert's troops.

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:48.920
How did you enter?

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:51.960
This is Mr. Ge, Leader of Cangmu Stronghold,

00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:54.000
-and this is Madam Ge. -Cangmu Stronghold?

00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:56.440
They're bandits?

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.600
Yes.

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:01.280
We broke in through the East Gate.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:03.520
There were roughly 500 Northern Desert soldiers there.

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.440
Madam Ge, you came at the perfect time.

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:11.240
If you need anything, just say the word.

00:04:12.600 --> 00:04:14.320
Let's return to the yamen for discussion.

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:23.040
Did you tell her?

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.240
Not a single word.

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:33.520
Madam Ge, you have come to our aid once again.

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.120
I am truly in your debt.

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:38.880
To fight against the pursuers from Xiaonan, we brought trouble upon you.

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:39.880
‎THE WAY OF HEAVEN, THE JUSTICE OF ALL

00:04:39.960 --> 00:04:42.720
Now, with Wangcheng in grave danger, we are dragging you into this yet again.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:44.800
You don't have to say that.

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:48.160
Bandits as we are, we do have a sense of honor.

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:50.320
With the enemy upon us, our fates are tied.

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:54.200
My promise to you all stands forever.

00:04:55.080 --> 00:04:55.920
We will never forget it.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:58.840
Your Highness is quite right.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:00.960
I searched the city and discovered over a dozen Northern Desert soldiers

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.680
And some weapons.

00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:03.640
They have all been seized.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.280
Mr. Zhao, the defense map.

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:06.200
‎Okay.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.720
The Northern Desert's troops advanced through Xiaonan.

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:12.600
Its mountain paths are treacherous,

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:15.240
Forcing them to travel light with their supplies and baggage.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:17.240
Therefore, compared to us,

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:19.760
-they will be far more agitated. -Indeed.

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:21.320
Just now on the city wall,

00:05:21.400 --> 00:05:23.720
The sound of the galloping was indeed erratic.

00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:26.200
Thus, they are desperate to take Wangcheng.

00:05:26.280 --> 00:05:28.240
They need a stronghold to resupply,

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:30.440
Then launch a pincer attack on Yunzhong.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:32.320
If Xiao Xun leads

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.880
The forces of Xiaonan Prefecture to reinforce the Northern Desert,

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:36.840
What should we do?

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:39.880
I know Xiao Xun.

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:42.920
Since he wants to use the Northern Desert as his weapon,

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.240
He will wait until the strike draws blood before coming into the light.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.800
He is waiting for their troops to occupy Wangcheng.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.040
The troops' passage through Xiaonan

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:53.720
Is the very proof of his sincerity to the Northern Desert.

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:56.160
Therefore, his men will not make any move for the time being.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:59.080
Three thousand against 800.

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:01.040
They still hold the upper hand.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.480
Wangcheng's defense resources are limited.

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:05.000
How are we to win?

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:06.400
My father once said

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:09.200
That fighting a war has never been about who has more troops.

00:06:10.200 --> 00:06:11.560
Now, I'll let them see

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:14.960
How the State of Chu defeats overwhelming odds.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:16.920
Well said, Your Highness.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.320
What plan do you have in mind?

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:22.880
Jiu, have you scouted out the enemy's provisions and water supply?

00:06:27.960 --> 00:06:30.520
To the east of Wangcheng, there is a stream.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:31.560
That is their water supply.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:34.760
To the west lie their provisions.

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:36.640
Their sentries are posted only in the open.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:42.400
Mr. Zhao, are there any branches or gorges upstream?

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:44.480
You want to cut off their water supply?

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:48.280
There is a waterway five li outside the city.

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:50.360
It dries up every dry season.

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:52.240
Diverting the water is feasible,

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:53.920
But we cannot dispatch laborers there right now.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.320
Leave this to me.

00:06:56.640 --> 00:06:58.480
-What's your plan? -Don't forget.

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:03.600
We can use bone whistles to contact our people outside the city

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:06.080
And have them take action at the waterway overnight.

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.560
Then I'll leave that to you.

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:10.680
You just mentioned a secret passage at the West Gate?

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:13.160
The passage leads right to this place.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:15.120
However, it was built during the late Emperor's reign

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:16.160
And has long been abandoned.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:19.960
Jiu, you said that their provisions are on the west side, right?

00:07:20.760 --> 00:07:21.680
Correct.

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:26.360
Then, even if it's an abandoned passage, we can still turn it to our advantage.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.880
Mr. Zhao, pass down the order.

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:30.200
All citizens must shut their doors.

00:07:30.280 --> 00:07:31.240
Any contact with the outside city is forbidden.

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:33.440
-Yes. -Furthermore,

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:37.160
Move all defense resources and provisions entirely to the South Gate.

00:07:37.760 --> 00:07:39.200
The enemy has the most troops at the North Gate,

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.560
Yet you are stacking the resources at the South Gate instead?

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.280
It's a diversion.

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:46.320
Right.

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:49.040
The city gates are all sealed. How are you going to pass the message

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:51.160
To lure the enemy into attacking the South Gate?

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:53.360
With 3,000 troops besieging the city,

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:57.440
They must assume the people inside are panicked and wavering.

00:07:57.520 --> 00:08:00.880
If, at this moment, someone defects with our defense map,

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:05.160
Do you think they'll believe it?

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:08.680
Desperate to breach the city, they won't be able to resist.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:15.920
But my act of cowardice won't fool them.

00:08:16.880 --> 00:08:18.080
I'll go.

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:25.240
You're just a scout.

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:26.480
How can you win the enemy's trust?

00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:32.720
Your Highness should know very well why I can win their trust, shouldn't you?

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:37.919
It has little chance of survival.

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.000
Have you thought it through?

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:40.640
I have.

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:43.640
-But I have one condition. -Insolent!

00:08:43.720 --> 00:08:46.200
With a formidable enemy upon us, how dare you propose conditions?

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:48.320
I know what you want.

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:51.000
If we win this battle and you come back alive,

00:08:51.080 --> 00:08:52.280
I will petition His Majesty to grant you a title.

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:57.240
Will the enemy truly believe the false intelligence he brings?

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.160
No.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.680
What I want him to take is the real defense map.

00:09:04.520 --> 00:09:07.680
After all, I did move the provisions to the South Gate.

00:09:08.520 --> 00:09:13.400
Nothing wins trust more easily than a lie woven with truth.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:23.320
Madam Ge, contact your men outside the city first.

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:26.240
Once the enemy verifies the defense map brought by Liang Qiang,

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.160
They will reinforce the South Gate.

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.480
The defenses at the West Gate will be weakened.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:33.360
Jiu, Mr. Ge, under the cover of night, leave the city by the secret passage,

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:36.000
Then burn their supplies and shatter their morale.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:39.480
Mr. Zhong, Madam Ge, watch for the fire as your signal.

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:40.480
Once the enemy is in total chaos,

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:43.160
Lead our 800 elite soldiers out from the North Gate to smash them.

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:44.640
Crush their main camp in one fell swoop,

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.480
Then rout the scattered troops one by one.

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:49.040
-Understood. -Understood.

00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:55.400
This battle is perilous.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:09:59.600
Everyone, please be careful.

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:01.520
-Yes. -Yes.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:05.800
VANGUARD BATTALION OF NORTHERN DESERT

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:09.480
General, should we launch the attack from the East and West Gates

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:13.160
And then lead the main force to crush the North Gate?

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:17.760
Report. We captured a spy at the South Gate.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:24.000
General, I have come to present Wangcheng's defense map.

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:41.960
They have only 500 garrison troops,

00:10:42.040 --> 00:10:44.000
All with outdated equipment and a lack of training.

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:46.880
The water supply east of Wangcheng has been cut off.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.640
It will dry up completely within a day.

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:52.240
All the city's provisions lie in the south.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:54.600
Right now, the defenses in the south are at their weakest.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:57.840
Attacking from the South Gate will ensure a swift capture of Wangcheng.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.640
Why would a turncoat like you help us?

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:06.680
‎PRISONER

00:11:07.280 --> 00:11:11.200
Because of a palace coup, my entire clan was unjustly exiled.

00:11:11.280 --> 00:11:13.360
The State of Chu treats me like worthless chaff.

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.720
Why should I remain loyal to it?

00:11:18.440 --> 00:11:20.640
Then what is your demand?

00:11:21.640 --> 00:11:23.160
If we successfully breach Wangcheng,

00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:26.960
I am willing to assist you, General, in attacking Yunzhong Prefecture,

00:11:27.560 --> 00:11:28.640
To replace Chu Ling.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:50.760
This is a diversion.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:54.360
You want to draw us to the South Gate, huh?

00:11:55.040 --> 00:11:56.520
Deceitful rat.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:59.120
-You deserve to die! -Report!

00:12:02.600 --> 00:12:03.800
General, the scouts report

00:12:03.880 --> 00:12:06.160
That Wangcheng's provisions are being moved to the South Gate.

00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:14.400
Take him down.

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:24.480
Move half the troops from the East and West Gates to the South Gate

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:27.320
And breach the city immediately!

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:28.320
-Yes! -Yes!

00:12:28.400 --> 00:12:30.160
‎WANGCHENG, YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

00:12:34.600 --> 00:12:38.000
WANGCHENG SOUTH GATE

00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:03.240
Quick!

00:13:04.080 --> 00:13:05.200
Hold the gate!

00:13:18.040 --> 00:13:20.720
Stand fast! I will reward five liang to everyone!

00:13:35.760 --> 00:13:36.840
Hurry!

00:13:36.920 --> 00:13:38.640
-Get over here! -Quick!

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:39.880
Hurry!

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:41.680
Quick! Hold the gate!

00:13:43.640 --> 00:13:44.480
Brace yourselves!

00:13:44.560 --> 00:13:45.400
‎Quick!

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:51.440
NORTHERN DESERT CAMP GRANARY

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:20.320
General, the granary is on fire.

00:14:20.400 --> 00:14:21.640
The State of Chu has burned our granary!

00:14:21.720 --> 00:14:22.640
What?

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:26.400
It's a trap! We've been duped!

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:28.440
Hear my command!

00:14:28.520 --> 00:14:30.720
Tonight, we must burn the city and seize their provisions!

00:14:30.800 --> 00:14:31.680
-Yes, General! -Yes, General!

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:34.800
Kill!

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.640
Soldiers! Let's trample the enemy's camp!

00:14:41.720 --> 00:14:42.880
WANGCHENG NORTH GATE

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:45.040
-Kill! -Kill!

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:49.480
‎WANGCHENG

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:02.000
WANGCHENG

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:16.040
Report!

00:15:16.760 --> 00:15:18.320
Report. The Northern Desert has retreated.

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:20.920
We slaughtered 2,000 of their men, though at the cost of 300 of our own.

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.480
General Zhong has led the troops back to the city.

00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:24.200
Good. Magnificent.

00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:25.440
‎JUSTICE HANGS ON HIGH

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:28.400
-Where is Xie Yanlai? -There is no word yet.

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:03.320
Hurry up.

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:06.920
Incoming!

00:18:11.720 --> 00:18:12.800
I promised

00:18:14.440 --> 00:18:15.880
I'd come back alive.

00:18:34.080 --> 00:18:35.800
CAPITAL

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:37.640
Victory at Wangcheng!

00:18:37.720 --> 00:18:40.520
The Grand Princess crushes the Northern Desert invaders!

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:43.040
-Victory at Wangcheng! -Come!

00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:45.760
The Grand Princess crushes the Northern Desert invaders!

00:18:46.680 --> 00:18:48.160
Victory at Wangcheng!

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:51.960
The Grand Princess crushes the Northern Desert invaders!

00:18:52.480 --> 00:18:54.360
Victory at Wangcheng!

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:57.520
The Grand Princess crushes the Northern Desert invaders!

00:18:57.600 --> 00:19:00.400
Miss Tang, what is going on?

00:19:00.480 --> 00:19:02.600
Why did Her Highness suddenly go to the frontier?

00:19:02.680 --> 00:19:04.720
This has been weighing on my heart for a long time.

00:19:04.800 --> 00:19:06.960
Today, I can finally speak of it.

00:19:07.040 --> 00:19:09.040
Do you know what Her Highness was doing

00:19:09.120 --> 00:19:12.120
While the entire Capital was cursing my uncle for incompetent leadership

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:14.400
And being too cowardly to advance?

00:19:15.240 --> 00:19:16.760
-What? -What was she doing?

00:19:16.840 --> 00:19:18.720
She rode a vast distance

00:19:18.800 --> 00:19:21.120
To save Wangcheng, crushing the Northern Desert's troops.

00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:22.800
Crushing the Northern Desert's troops?

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:24.080
This is what the Chu clan does.

00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:26.800
We defend the nation, heedless of blame or death.

00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:30.080
We do not speak of it. We act.

00:19:30.160 --> 00:19:32.680
No. You cannot stay silent anymore.

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:36.680
You bore it all when General Chu was slandered.

00:19:36.760 --> 00:19:39.280
But now, Her Highness has achieved a glorious victory.

00:19:39.360 --> 00:19:40.360
She must not be forgotten.

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:43.920
Tang, host a banquet at the Chu Mansion and send out the invitations.

00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.520
Let everyone in the Capital come to praise Her Highness.

00:19:47.960 --> 00:19:50.840
And let those who love to gossip behind her back

00:19:51.560 --> 00:19:54.360
Take a good look at what kind of extraordinary figure

00:19:54.440 --> 00:19:56.240
Her Highness truly is.

00:19:56.320 --> 00:19:57.360
I will head back right now

00:19:57.440 --> 00:19:58.320
And have my father write a memorial of congratulation.

00:19:58.400 --> 00:20:00.000
What's wrong with you?

00:20:00.080 --> 00:20:01.840
She deserves a congratulatory memorial.

00:20:01.920 --> 00:20:03.560
She is the Grand Princess, after all.

00:20:03.640 --> 00:20:05.400
-Yes, a congratulatory memorial. -Indeed.

00:20:05.480 --> 00:20:06.320
Let's go.

00:20:06.880 --> 00:20:08.040
My princess.

00:20:09.080 --> 00:20:10.480
You do not fight for fame,

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.200
But you will have every bit of the glory you deserve.

00:20:15.080 --> 00:20:18.120
Your Majesty, this morning, a top-urgent dispatch arrived.

00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:19.960
It reports that Her Highness has relieved the siege of Wangcheng

00:20:20.040 --> 00:20:22.120
And crushed the Northern Desert forces.

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:24.880
Her Highness absented herself on the pretext of illness,

00:20:24.960 --> 00:20:29.120
Yet she violated palace decrees by fleeing to fight at the frontier.

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.200
This is sheer absurdity.

00:20:31.280 --> 00:20:34.640
Mr. Deng and Mr. Xie serve as imperial councilors.

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:36.640
To permit such misconduct is a dereliction of duty.

00:20:36.720 --> 00:20:38.880
-They ought to-- -Ought to what?

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:42.600
Ministers, may I remind you

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:44.560
His Majesty was saved by none other than Her Highness,

00:20:44.640 --> 00:20:47.080
Who rode into battle to slay the rebels?

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:49.440
Her Highness privately mobilized the army.

00:20:49.520 --> 00:20:51.360
What does she take the laws to be?

00:20:51.960 --> 00:20:55.240
As Regent, how could you allow this indulgence?

00:20:55.320 --> 00:20:56.160
Indulgence?

00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:59.120
I would ask you all instead.

00:20:59.920 --> 00:21:01.080
Who was it

00:21:01.680 --> 00:21:04.560
Who stood in this very court and vehemently denounced

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:06.040
The incompetence of the Guard General?

00:21:06.760 --> 00:21:07.880
And who was it

00:21:07.960 --> 00:21:11.600
Who petitioned daily for reinforcements?

00:21:11.680 --> 00:21:14.400
Now that Her Highness has lifted the siege on the frontier,

00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:17.520
You are suddenly displeased.

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:18.760
Preposterous!

00:21:18.840 --> 00:21:22.440
Since when has the State of Chu relied upon women to lead armies?

00:21:22.520 --> 00:21:26.320
If we have truly come to such a pass, though old and frail,

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:28.320
I would gladly march to my death.

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:31.760
When His Majesty first ascended the throne,

00:21:31.840 --> 00:21:35.040
It was Her Highness who slew the traitors to protect him.

00:21:35.120 --> 00:21:38.280
By that right alone, she may defend the frontier.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:41.920
If you are truly devoted to the state,

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:45.120
You are welcome to depart immediately for the frontier.

00:21:45.200 --> 00:21:47.480
Mr. Deng and I shall certainly not hinder you.

00:21:47.560 --> 00:21:49.600
You You

00:21:49.680 --> 00:21:51.920
Please calm your wrath.

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.840
It was merely a suggestion.

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:59.720
Ministers, lend ear to my words.

00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:04.040
I owe my survival in troubled times to the Grand Princess's protection.

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:07.520
She is the daughter of Guard General Chu Ling.

00:22:07.600 --> 00:22:10.600
Though a woman, she is valiant and skilled in warfare.

00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:14.840
Thus, my grandfather bestowed upon her as Grand Princess of State

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:18.080
So she might continue to safeguard my security.

00:22:18.680 --> 00:22:21.600
As the Son of Heaven, I preside over the imperial city,

00:22:21.680 --> 00:22:24.440
Unable to go to the frontier to save the state and protect the people.

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:28.120
Therefore, I requested the Grand Princess to go to the frontier

00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:30.080
To relieve my burden.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:37.640
This is no absurdity.

00:22:37.720 --> 00:22:39.200
It was the late Emperor's decree.

00:22:39.920 --> 00:22:41.960
Let no official presume to speculate further.

00:22:42.040 --> 00:22:44.800
The Grand Princess leaving the palace was by my command.

00:22:45.560 --> 00:22:46.880
However,

00:22:48.000 --> 00:22:50.600
How did 3,000 Northern Desert soldiers suddenly appear at Wangcheng?

00:22:51.200 --> 00:22:54.160
They bypassed our entire frontier and pressed straight to the city walls.

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:56.320
-Mr. Deng. -Yes, Your Majesty.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:57.960
Order the Ministry of War to investigate.

00:22:58.560 --> 00:23:01.040
From whence did these soldiers come?

00:23:01.640 --> 00:23:03.800
Is it a lapse in our frontier defenses,

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:05.200
Or ?

00:23:06.840 --> 00:23:08.960
This matter must be accounted for to the fallen soldiers.

00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:11.560
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:23:12.560 --> 00:23:14.520
Let there be no further debate or censure on this matter.

00:23:14.600 --> 00:23:17.680
The Grand Princess's great victory is a joyous occasion for the state.

00:23:17.760 --> 00:23:18.600
It warrants celebration.

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:21.160
-Congratulations to Your Majesty -Congratulations to Your Majesty

00:23:21.240 --> 00:23:23.920
-and to Her Highness. -and to Her Highness.

00:23:27.960 --> 00:23:28.800
Zhao,

00:23:30.280 --> 00:23:31.120
Finally,

00:23:32.280 --> 00:23:33.560
I can protect you.

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:37.840
IN HARMONY WITH YIN AND YANG

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:41.960
<i>Zhao won the highest merit</i> <i>in the great victory at Wangcheng.</i>

00:23:42.040 --> 00:23:45.000
<i>I will surely hold my head high</i> <i>before Mr. Deng.</i>

00:23:45.600 --> 00:23:49.000
<i>Even so, I showed disrespect</i> <i>to him before.</i>

00:23:49.080 --> 00:23:51.200
<i>It would not be surprising</i> <i>if he took offense.</i>

00:23:51.720 --> 00:23:55.280
<i>According to Zhao, he's a sly fox,</i> <i>but a dutiful son.</i>

00:23:56.080 --> 00:23:59.080
<i>Currying favor with his mother</i> <i>is the best way to win him over.</i>

00:24:00.040 --> 00:24:01.800
Miss Tang, to what do I owe the pleasure?

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:04.800
Did you come because of Her Highness's victory,

00:24:04.880 --> 00:24:06.520
Just to gloat before my eyes?

00:24:07.800 --> 00:24:09.120
Not at all.

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:11.800
I heard your mother has had a persistent cough,

00:24:12.400 --> 00:24:14.000
So I brought some <i>Chuanbei</i>.

00:24:15.440 --> 00:24:16.640
Zhao told me.

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:25.120
Is that Miss Chu?

00:24:25.800 --> 00:24:26.640
Mother.

00:24:26.720 --> 00:24:28.560
-Yi. -Easy.

00:24:29.800 --> 00:24:30.840
Here.

00:24:30.920 --> 00:24:36.160
I had the millet you sent simmered into congee by the servants.

00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:38.240
Paired with some pickled vegetables,

00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:40.920
It truly tastes like my hometown.

00:24:41.000 --> 00:24:43.920
Old Madam, I am Chu

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:45.560
I know. Chu Zhao.

00:24:47.120 --> 00:24:48.600
-Yi. -Mother.

00:24:48.680 --> 00:24:51.240
Miss Chu came here again and again with gifts.

00:24:51.320 --> 00:24:53.240
How could you not even offer a cup of tea?

00:24:53.320 --> 00:24:57.480
Mother, this is Chu Tang, not Chu Zhao.

00:24:57.560 --> 00:25:00.720
Madam, I am Zhao's elder cousin.

00:25:00.800 --> 00:25:01.640
My name is Chu Tang.

00:25:02.280 --> 00:25:03.360
-Chu -I came specifically

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:04.920
To pay my respects to you.

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:07.320
Have Madam back for her medicine. Go.

00:25:07.920 --> 00:25:09.680
Mother, it is time you took your medicine.

00:25:10.320 --> 00:25:11.240
Alright.

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:14.000
The young ladies of the Chu Family are both good girls.

00:25:14.720 --> 00:25:16.000
Do not miss this opportunity.

00:25:17.800 --> 00:25:19.880
Miss Chu, do visit again.

00:25:21.080 --> 00:25:23.560
They are both good girls. Good girls.

00:25:25.960 --> 00:25:29.400
Madam must have misunderstood something.

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:33.240
My mother is sometimes a bit confused.

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:34.360
My apologies.

00:25:34.440 --> 00:25:37.440
Since the gifts have been delivered, I shall not intrude any further.

00:25:37.520 --> 00:25:38.400
Farewell.

00:25:39.800 --> 00:25:44.360
CHARTING THE COSMOS

00:25:51.240 --> 00:25:54.760
Zhao has foiled my plans once again.

00:25:55.360 --> 00:25:58.080
After this battle, the Northern Desert King lost over 2,500 men.

00:25:58.160 --> 00:26:00.480
The surviving soldiers seek passage through Xiaonan Prefecture

00:26:00.560 --> 00:26:01.400
To return to the Northern Desert.

00:26:04.160 --> 00:26:09.560
Since they have been defeated, those survivors need not go back.

00:26:11.240 --> 00:26:12.440
Your Highness, you mean?

00:26:14.240 --> 00:26:18.080
Slaughter every last one of them.

00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:20.560
The court wishes to investigate?

00:26:21.760 --> 00:26:23.720
Then we'll let them find nothing but dead ends.

00:26:24.560 --> 00:26:26.520
Should the Northern Desert King learn our hand was behind this

00:26:26.600 --> 00:26:28.280
Dead men tell no tales.

00:26:29.640 --> 00:26:33.720
Those remnants may not survive the journey back.

00:26:34.560 --> 00:26:36.280
And even if some escape,

00:26:38.240 --> 00:26:40.680
Who could prove it was our doing?

00:26:42.640 --> 00:26:43.680
Yes.

00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:57.680
Zhao,

00:26:59.800 --> 00:27:02.280
You trampled upon my heart.

00:27:04.600 --> 00:27:10.320
Then do not blame me for showing you no mercy hereafter.

00:27:10.400 --> 00:27:11.520
XIE RESIDENCE

00:27:11.600 --> 00:27:12.600
Mr. Xie,

00:27:12.680 --> 00:27:14.720
Her Highness has dispatched riders to report the victory at Wangcheng

00:27:14.800 --> 00:27:16.640
Back to the Capital with all haste.

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:18.520
It seems her ambitions run deep.

00:27:20.000 --> 00:27:23.840
All of this is fact, with not a word of exaggeration.

00:27:25.360 --> 00:27:28.200
It was she who led the troops and routed the Northern Desert's forces,

00:27:28.280 --> 00:27:29.760
Delivering the people of Wangcheng.

00:27:30.360 --> 00:27:33.200
A merit this great deserves to be proclaimed far and wide.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:37.680
It would settle the hearts of the people and bring stability to the realm.

00:27:38.280 --> 00:27:41.040
Were she a man, there would be nothing wrong with this.

00:27:41.680 --> 00:27:43.760
Were she a general, even if it was Chu Ling,

00:27:43.840 --> 00:27:45.440
There would be nothing wrong with it either.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:49.280
But she is a woman.

00:27:49.360 --> 00:27:51.920
And now that she has become the Grand Princess,

00:27:52.000 --> 00:27:55.920
Should she not remain in the Capital, living out her days in virtuous nobility?

00:27:56.000 --> 00:27:58.600
Why must she seek such glory on the battlefield?

00:27:58.680 --> 00:28:02.560
She rules alongside His Majesty and attends the court with His Majesty.

00:28:02.640 --> 00:28:05.080
At every turn, she stands before the ministers.

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:07.160
And now, she intends to stand before the whole world.

00:28:07.240 --> 00:28:11.640
Clearly, she refuses to know her place and means to usurp the throne.

00:28:11.720 --> 00:28:14.320
She's obviously taking advantage of Yu's age.

00:28:14.400 --> 00:28:16.680
What is there to be vexed about?

00:28:17.600 --> 00:28:20.160
What she guards with her life is Yu's state.

00:28:20.840 --> 00:28:23.200
Technically, I'm her uncle, too.

00:28:23.800 --> 00:28:26.600
We're family, right?

00:28:31.680 --> 00:28:33.240
Yanlai was right, though.

00:28:35.640 --> 00:28:37.200
She's sharper

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:42.600
Than I imagined.

00:28:45.320 --> 00:28:48.680
WANGCHENG

00:29:21.760 --> 00:29:23.480
In defense of Wangcheng,

00:29:24.720 --> 00:29:26.160
800 soldiers marched out,

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:29.040
But barely 500 returned.

00:29:30.680 --> 00:29:35.400
Yet the tens of thousands of its people survived.

00:29:38.280 --> 00:29:40.560
Behind every fallen soldier

00:29:43.280 --> 00:29:45.720
Are children waiting for their fathers,

00:29:47.040 --> 00:29:49.200
Aging mothers straining for a glimpse of their sons,

00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:55.400
And wives aching for their husbands.

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:00.400
But they are never coming back.

00:30:07.160 --> 00:30:08.520
Your father once told me

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:12.720
That we wage war

00:30:15.080 --> 00:30:17.280
Only so that more people may live.

00:30:18.560 --> 00:30:20.200
I, too, once sought death,

00:30:23.200 --> 00:30:25.760
But it was he who showed me the purpose of staying alive.

00:30:27.360 --> 00:30:31.120
The living will greet a better tomorrow,

00:30:32.240 --> 00:30:35.120
But they will forever remember those who fell.

00:30:36.320 --> 00:30:40.520
This is the meaning of their sacrifice.

00:30:52.960 --> 00:30:54.040
Their deaths

00:30:56.440 --> 00:31:00.200
Are the fault of war and of these chaotic times.

00:31:04.200 --> 00:31:05.640
Not yours.

00:31:10.600 --> 00:31:11.440
Zhao.

00:31:37.120 --> 00:31:39.080
CAPITAL

00:31:39.160 --> 00:31:41.720
In broad daylight, how can you lynch him?

00:31:49.080 --> 00:31:50.200
They're killing him casually!

00:31:50.280 --> 00:31:52.400
Zhao, be good.

00:31:54.800 --> 00:31:59.200
<i>Perhaps you don't know</i> <i>what your name means to me.</i>

00:31:59.880 --> 00:32:01.520
<i>But just as dawn</i> <i>always drives away the night,</i>

00:32:02.840 --> 00:32:06.160
<i>you saved me.</i>

00:32:10.280 --> 00:32:11.680
<i>After you left,</i>

00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:14.440
<i>I kept searching for you</i> <i>wherever your trail led.</i>

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:19.000
<i>Back then, I thought</i> <i>if I couldn't survive,</i>

00:32:19.080 --> 00:32:22.560
<i>dying where you were wouldn't be so bad.</i>

00:32:31.280 --> 00:32:32.760
So, that young man

00:32:35.720 --> 00:32:36.560
Was you.

00:32:38.360 --> 00:32:39.280
Yes.

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:51.760
Zhao.

00:32:54.520 --> 00:32:55.720
You were the one

00:32:58.240 --> 00:33:01.240
Who pulled me out of the abyss.

00:33:02.760 --> 00:33:03.960
It was you

00:33:06.040 --> 00:33:07.640
Who gave me a reason to live.

00:33:13.360 --> 00:33:14.760
You always asked me

00:33:17.720 --> 00:33:19.400
Why I kept saying I owed you.

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:23.400
This is

00:33:24.880 --> 00:33:25.880
The reason.

00:33:40.360 --> 00:33:41.320
So

00:33:44.320 --> 00:33:45.160
From now on,

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:47.600
My life

00:33:49.640 --> 00:33:50.600
Is yours.

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:43.719
<i>Your merits are reported,</i>

00:34:44.320 --> 00:34:47.840
<i>your name has been cleared,</i> <i>and rewards will follow.</i>

00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:59.200
How is the situation outside the city?

00:34:59.280 --> 00:35:01.680
Your Highness, the remnants are cleared.

00:35:01.760 --> 00:35:03.360
Three Northern Desert maps are seized.

00:35:13.080 --> 00:35:15.160
Wangcheng wouldn't have held without your efforts.

00:35:15.760 --> 00:35:17.560
General Zhong has transferred me to the Vanguard Battalion.

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:19.480
I am immensely grateful.

00:35:20.320 --> 00:35:21.160
The Wei Village?

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:24.760
What is the meaning of this marking?

00:35:25.640 --> 00:35:26.840
I do not know.

00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:29.400
But since the Northern Desert scouts made this mark,

00:35:30.000 --> 00:35:32.280
It stands to reason that this village must hold some significance.

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:37.520
That name sounds familiar.

00:35:46.600 --> 00:35:49.080
‎WEI VILLAGE

00:35:52.480 --> 00:35:54.960
Help!

00:35:55.040 --> 00:35:57.800
Please help us!

00:35:58.320 --> 00:36:01.840
Someone help!

00:36:02.960 --> 00:36:05.960
Please, save us!

00:36:09.400 --> 00:36:11.840
Is anyone there?

00:36:11.920 --> 00:36:14.800
Help!

00:36:42.360 --> 00:36:43.600
Leaving already?

00:36:44.800 --> 00:36:46.000
I'm no soldier.

00:36:46.080 --> 00:36:48.560
Guarding the city is not my job.

00:36:51.880 --> 00:36:54.680
Take good care of her, will you?

00:36:54.760 --> 00:36:58.000
Of course I will. I've watched her grow up.

00:37:03.560 --> 00:37:04.640
Is he doing well?

00:37:06.040 --> 00:37:06.880
He's alive.

00:37:13.400 --> 00:37:17.000
If he passes away, send for me at once.

00:37:17.600 --> 00:37:18.760
Are you leaving?

00:37:23.520 --> 00:37:24.960
I owe you a great debt for your aid this time.

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:27.840
I was hoping you might return with us to Yunzhong Prefecture.

00:37:28.840 --> 00:37:30.080
No.

00:37:30.160 --> 00:37:31.840
I have been away from the stronghold too long.

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:32.760
It is time I returned.

00:37:43.920 --> 00:37:45.440
If you need me ever again,

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:48.120
Send word to Cangmu Stronghold.

00:38:02.600 --> 00:38:06.600
We haven't yet received orders from higher up. Not sure about this battle.

00:38:07.320 --> 00:38:11.600
I believe it all depends on the situation in Wangcheng.

00:38:12.760 --> 00:38:14.960
-No news yet. -Indeed.

00:38:15.560 --> 00:38:16.920
About the battle in Wangcheng

00:38:17.000 --> 00:38:19.680
Where did 3,000 Northern Desert soldiers come from?

00:38:19.760 --> 00:38:21.200
We can only hope

00:38:23.560 --> 00:38:24.400
‎Do we really

00:38:25.000 --> 00:38:27.280
Do we really have no faith in our own troops?

00:38:35.960 --> 00:38:39.360
-This whole thing feels off. -It is still possible.

00:38:39.440 --> 00:38:41.320
How did this happen?

00:38:43.440 --> 00:38:45.320
How did they bypassed our frontier?

00:38:45.400 --> 00:38:46.520
Report!

00:38:47.720 --> 00:38:49.160
General, a great victory at Wangcheng!

00:38:49.240 --> 00:38:50.080
Her Highness led the army

00:38:50.160 --> 00:38:51.240
And drove back the Northern Desert vanguard.

00:38:51.320 --> 00:38:52.320
Over a thousand enemies slain.

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:54.040
A strong father raises no weak daughter.

00:38:54.120 --> 00:38:55.400
Present the dispatch.

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:01.920
General, Her Highness fought a glorious battle.

00:39:02.440 --> 00:39:03.840
We should welcome her return in triumph.

00:39:04.440 --> 00:39:06.520
She has brought such honor to us.

00:39:06.600 --> 00:39:07.880
Indeed.

00:39:07.960 --> 00:39:10.360
General, Her Highness's arrival at Yunzhong Prefecture

00:39:10.440 --> 00:39:11.440
Is a great boost to morale.

00:39:11.520 --> 00:39:13.080
I will ready the ceremonial guard right now.

00:39:13.160 --> 00:39:14.760
-Exactly. -No need.

00:39:16.440 --> 00:39:19.840
The one returning is not the Grand Princess,

00:39:21.360 --> 00:39:24.480
But my daughter, Zhao.

00:39:25.320 --> 00:39:28.280
I am willing to lead the light cavalry to escort Miss Zhao back.

00:39:28.360 --> 00:39:30.600
She knows the roads better than any of you.

00:39:31.480 --> 00:39:33.080
Go and rest your troops.

00:39:34.200 --> 00:39:35.680
Do not delay the greater matters at hand.

00:39:36.640 --> 00:39:37.720
You may withdraw.

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:39.920
-Yes! -Yes!

00:40:37.240 --> 00:40:39.520
<i>I really wish I could see you.</i>

00:40:42.840 --> 00:40:44.400
<i>Zhao.</i>

